{"article_id":"UNKdpqHYCqyl7oiA","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Protesters hold placards at a demonstration","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"demanding Hong Kong ' s leaders to step down","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"and withdraw the extradition bill","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"in Hong Kong , China , June 16 , 2019 .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"( Athit Perawongmetha/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":5,"text":"If you need an example of man ' s desire","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"to be free ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"and his willingness","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to resist tyranny ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"look to the streets of Hong Kong .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Some 2 million residents of the city gathered there , in protest .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"The population of the city is only 7.3 million .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"It was a stirring sight","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"- one of the most stirring","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"the world has seen in recent years .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"The protests in Tiananmen Square were stirring , too .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"That was exactly 30 years ago .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"It ended in a massacre of protesters by the Communist authorities .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Every Hong Konger in the streets this year knew that .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"The immediate object of their protest was an extradition bill ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"which would have sent Hong Kongers","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"accused of a crime","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"to the mainland , for trial .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"On the mainland , there is nothing like justice .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Instead , there is torture , a sham trial , and a gulag","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"( called laogai ) .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Yet the protest in Hong Kong had a more general object .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Citizens are intent on keeping their freedoms ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"or not letting them go","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"without a fight .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"When the British turned over the city to the Chinese Communist Party in 1997 ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"the promise was \" one country , two systems , \" for 50 years .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"This was always chimerical .","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Year by year , month by month , the CCP has been chipping away at Hong Kong ' s autonomy .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"The Party will not tolerate Hong Kong ' s brash , uppity independence until 2047 .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Five years ago , democratic protests broke out .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"These were dubbed the \" umbrella movement , \"","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"because people used umbrellas","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"to shield themselves from pepper spray .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Earlier this year , eight leaders of the movement were sentenced .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"One of them , Chan Kin-man , a retired sociology professor , said ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"\" In the verdict , the judge commented","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that we are naïve \"","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"( naïve to believe","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that a protest movement can attain , or retain , democracy ) .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"\" But what is more naïve than believing in one country , two systems ? \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"In Taiwan , there were street protests in behalf of the umbrella-movement leaders","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"sentenced .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Why ?","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"Because Taiwanese know","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"that their fate , and their democracy , is linked to Hong Kong .","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"In the wake of the extradition bill , the umbrellas came out again ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"as people tried to shield themselves from pepper spray , tear gas , and rubber bullets .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Faced with this massive demonstration ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"which caught the attention of the world ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Hong Kong officials backed down .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The chief executive , Carrie Lam , announced the suspension of the extradition bill ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"and even offered an apology for its introduction .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Some protest leaders demanded her resignation .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Others pointed out","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that whoever followed her would be in the same position","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"- a servant of Xi Jinping , the PRC ' s supreme leader","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"( for life ) .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"\" Hong Kong ' s bravery has bought it some time. \"","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"So said Edward Lucas , the British foreign-affairs analyst ,","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and he put it well .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"We think back to \" Finlandization , \"","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"which is often misunderstood .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Finlandization was the process","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"by which Finland was rendered essentially neutral in the Cold War .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"The Finns did not set out to be Finlandized ;","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"they wished to be with the Free West .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"They fought like hell","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"to avoid Sovietization ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"which resulted in their ( mere ) Finlandization .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"In a similar vein , Hong Kongers are fighting like hell","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"to keep the noose relatively loose around their necks .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"They are fighting","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"to retain a little breathing space .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"The ruling Communists in Beijing hate the example of Hong Kong ,","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"as they hate the example of","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"( even worse )","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Taiwan .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"They don ' t want other Chinese","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"- more than a billion of them -","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to get ideas :","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"ideas","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that Chinese people , in some places , can live freely and democratically .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"News of the drama in Hong Kong was blocked on the mainland .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"Asked to comment on this drama ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"President Trump said ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"\" I hope","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"it all works out for China and for Hong Kong .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"I understand the reason for the demonstration ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"but I ' m sure","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"they will be able to work it out. \"","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"The United States can do better than this .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"People look to us for leadership , for moral support ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"and we should provide it","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"whenever possible .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Maybe Hong Kongers are doing nothing more","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"than delaying the inevitable -","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"their eventual subjugation by the PRC .","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"If so ,","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"they are still doing something inspiring , right , and brave .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":209,"left":109,"right":208,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":107,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":0,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":138,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":138,"left":133,"right":137,"relation":"el